{"type":"message","id":"fa0543d0","parentId":"7f199eb7","timestamp":"2026-03-04T03:18:05.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"QVeris工具的参数传递似乎有问题。让我换一个思路 - 看看EODHD返回的完整数据，看看有没有类似\"views\"或者\"engagement\"的字段。让我重新调用EODHD新闻并查看更多返回的字段。\n\n或者，也许用户说的\"热度\"是指sentiment的polarity值？让我看看EODHD数据中sentiment的极性值，筛选polarity较高（热度高）的新闻。\n\n从之前的数据来看，sentiment包含:\n- polarity: 从-1到1，越高表示越正面\n- neg, neu, pos: 各种情绪比例\n\n但这似乎不是\"热度\"的概念。\n\n让我尝试搜索finnhub特有的\"热度\"指标，或者直接用EODHD数据筛选出一些高热度新闻。","thinkingSignature":"1bd3ab19f6559819230aa28e95bd86ee2544e780f4289acea069af5b994a9870"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hbj20wofvrm7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs search \"finnhub news heat score popularity\" --limit 5","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":22529,"output":221,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36734,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772594278334}}
{"type":"message","id":"0e984e7d","parentId":"fa0543d0","timestamp":"2026-03-04T03:18:11.247Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hbj20wofvrm7_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"finnhub news heat score popularity\",\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.sentiments.retrieve.v1.c2c27d35\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Sentiment Data\",\n      \"description\": \"Get sentiment scores for one or more financial instruments (stocks, ETFs, crypto) calculated from news and social media, normalized on a scale from -1 (very negative) to 1 (very positive).\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"One or more comma-separated tickers, for example: AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"s\": \"AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1240.63,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.779\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method for results.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 538.66,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.734\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function name.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 672.29,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.893\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.companynews.retrieve.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Company News\",\n      \"description\": \"List latest company news by symbol. This endpoint is only available for North American companies.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Company symbol.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"From date <code>YYYY-MM-DD</code>.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"To date <code>YYYY-MM-DD</code>.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"to\": \"2025-11-24\",\n          \"from\": \"2025-11-17\",\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"